headline.main: Tennis: Cuevas Wins to Set Up Third Consecutive Final in Brazil
headline.print_headline: Tennis: Cuevas Wins to Set Up Third Consecutive Final in Brazil

lead_paragraph: Pablo Cuevas beat Spanish top seed Pablo Carreno Busta 6-3 7-6(2) on Saturday to set himself for a chance of a third consecutive Brasil Open title.
